<li><a href="https://auth0.com/blog/2015/10/06/getting-started-with-relay/">Getting Started with Relay</a> - One of the few detailed walk throughs of hand-on Relay.</li>
<li><a href="https://medium.com/@clayallsopp/relay-101-building-a-hacker-news-client-bb8b2bdc76e6#.1i64q1pf9">Relay 101: Building A Hacker News Client</a> - A complete workable example.
